name: covid-19-dashboard
description: ``` sudo su cd covid19-dasboard npm install express npm install concat-stream cd node_modules git clone https://github.com/qmshao/covid19-dblib.git cd covid-dblib npm install cd ../../ npm install pm2 -g mkdir ~/.aws vim ~/.aws/credentials pm2 start dashdb.js -i max ```
author: Quan Min Shao
